<title>USA: Newpark Resources Q4 net rises.</title>
<headline>Newpark Resources Q4 net rises.</headline>
<dateline>METAIRIE, La. 1997-03-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>(in 000's except per share amounts)</p>
<p>					    Quarter Ended  Year Ended</p>
<p>					     December 31   December 30</p>
<p>					1996	1995  1996(a) 1995(b)</p>
<p> Revenues			$40,045   $28,526 $121,542 $97,982</p>
<p> Operating income	     12,125     6,951   31,840  20,980</p>
<p> Net income			7,471     3,840   18,453  12,236</p>
<p>Net income per common share</p>
<p>and common equivalent share:</p>
<p>   Primary			  0.50	0.35     1.46    1.13</p>
<p>   Fully diluted		  0.50	0.35     1.46    1.13</p>
<p>Weighted average and common</p>
<p>equivalent shares outstanding</p>
<p>   Primary			14,953    10,894   12,616  10,828</p>
<p>   Fully diluted		14,973    11,003   12,666  10,870</p>
<p>(a) 1996 net income includes the effect of a nonrecurring charge of $2.4 million, equal to $0.12 per primary and fully diluted share.</p>
<p>(b) 1995 net income includes the effect of a nonrecurring charge of $436,000, equal to $0.02 per primary and fully diluted share.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212 859-1610</p>
</text>
